    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kitchen cabinets in which food is stored, having a ventilated front, generally of pierced tin or sometimes of screening or cloth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
